I"G<p>The body seeks balance and sustainable resource use. <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/breathwork-modulates-autonomic-arousal">Lack of oxygen</a>, <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/affect-reflects-ideological-structures">conflicting beliefs</a>, <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/peer-pressure-modulates-autonomic-arousal">social pressure</a>, and other stressors trigger anxiety, a drive for regaining homeostasis. However, a careful usage of <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/agitation-can-be-weaponized">stressors can be useful</a>.</p>
